  dif t$. Then

  $
    dif EE[L^z_t (a)] = epsilon P^((z))(a, t) tilde(b)^2(t, x_t, lambda_t) dif t,
  $
  where $P^((z))(a, t)$ denotes the density of $z_t$ at level $a$.
